00:49:34,380 --> 00:49:42,780
♫ Many tears were shed and there were many arguments ♫

594
00:49:42,780 --> 00:49:46,680
♫ Above all, thank you for your irreplaceable time, ♫

595
00:49:46,680 --> 00:49:53,340
♫  your smile, and today ♫

596
00:49:53,340 --> 00:50:01,710
♫ and there were many arguments and there were many arguments ♫

597
00:50:01,710 --> 00:50:10,200
♫ Above all, there's the irreplaceable time, your smile, and surely tomorrow as well ♫

598
00:50:10,200 --> 00:50:18,510
♫ Your memories and your future,
Hold onto them tightly, so they won't be ruined ♫

599
00:50:18,510 --> 00:50:29,770
♫ More than anyone else, I always want to walk by your side ♫

600
00:50:31,030 --> 00:50:33,660
Um, can I come to the party as well?

601
00:50:33,660 --> 00:50:35,480
Christmas is so great!

602
00:50:35,480 --> 00:50:38,350
We will have a party to celebrate on Christmas Eve.

603
00:50:38,350 --> 00:50:42,260
I heard you can't go... because you will spend
Christmas with your girlfriends.

604
00:50:42,260 --> 00:50:45,070
Boyfriends? When did that happen to both of you?

605
00:50:45,070 --> 00:50:47,080
Kotoko is going to be alone.

606
00:50:47,080 --> 00:50:50,100
It's okay that I can't be with Irie-kun.

607
00:50:50,100 --> 00:50:54,690
-A thief has been breaking into houses around here.
-Huh?

608
00:50:56,750 --> 00:51:01,210
-It's a big deal!
-You! You! You!
